Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: NewMarket Square is Wichita’s vibrant lifestyle destination and home to popular national and local retailers and restaurants. Located on the thriving Maize Road corridor, NewMarket Square is situated in a high-growth submarket, supported by a well-educated and affluent customer base. As the area’s largest outdoor shopping center, it offers a strong retail mix and provides the only west side location for a multitude of tenants. With a strong anchor tenant lineup, critical mass of retail, growing primary market area, young family consumer base with strong demographics, high occupancy,and robust sales, NewMarket Square is primed for future success and expansion.
